// ─── 2.1 Common fields and why they matter ─────────────────────────────────
//  Your project uses playwright.config.js (JavaScript config).
//  If you use TypeScript config, filename becomes playwright.config.ts.
//
//  Common fields:
//    testDir        : Folder containing tests.
